POProcurementCardApproval_ST is a SecurityClass
	description is "Approval of Procurement Card Transactions"
	Access Rights
		
		po Module 
			is accessible
				for all actions
				unconditionally
		
		ProcurementCardStatementTransaction BusinessClass
			is accessible
				for all actions
				when (ProcurementCardStatementTransaction.Company.SecurityGroupAllowsAccess)
		ProcurementCardStatementTransactionDistribution BusinessClass
			is accessible
				for all actions
				when (ProcurementCardStatementTransaction.Company.SecurityGroupAllowsAccess)
		ProcurementCardStatementTransactionComment BusinessClass
			is accessible
				for all actions
				when (ProcurementCardStatementTransaction.Company.SecurityGroupAllowsAccess)						
		ApproveProcurementCardTransactions MenuItem for RequesterMenu Menu
			is accessible 
				for all actions
				unconditionally
